For
                example: cat /var/lib/kubelet/cpu_manager_state | jq
{
  "policyName": "static",
  "defaultCpuSet": "0-1,7-11",
  "entries": {
    "915d338f-c013-4984-a53c-51db78476dbf": {
      "contrail-vrouter-agent-dpdk": "2-6",
      "contrail-vrouter-kernel-init-dpdk": "2"
    }
  },
  "checksum": 3199431349
}


You'll need to install jq (dnf install -y jq)
                  in order to see formatted output.
